               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PAYNE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How near were you to him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I had hold of the collar of his coat—I am footman to Mr. Barker, in Ca-dogan-place, Chelsea—I am sure I saw it in the prisoner's hand—there was another person crossing the road too—he was pushing the handker<lb></lb>chief into a box bush while I had bold of him.</p>
